<keyLead pageId="81" pageNumber="81">
12. Femora reddish orange on apical halves; male genitalia as in figure 26A–N........................... 
<taxonomicName authority="Knight" authorityName="Knight" box="[990,1228,1630,1650]" class="Insecta" family="Miridae" genus="Slaterocoris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="81" pageNumber="81" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rubrofemoratus">
