</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="82" pageNumber="82">
<paragraph blockId="82.[93,620,212,1758]" pageId="82" pageNumber="82">
<keyLead pageId="82" pageNumber="82">
18. Femora with from basal quarters to halves black with remainder dark orange-red; dorsal vestiture shining golden, short, and reclining; male genitalia as in figure 21A– 
